Direct Known Subclasses:
ArrayAccess, NamedVariable
public abstract sealed class Variable extends Node permits ArrayAccess, NamedVariable
This class is the abstract superclass of any variable in an SPL program.

A variable is either a simple named variable (NamedVariable) or an array access (ArrayAccess). Every variable has a semantic Type which has to be filled in during phase 4.
